<article index="true">
    <topic>
        <title>&lt;DateComboBox&gt;</title>
        <p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <b>&lt;DateComboBox/&gt;</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li><b>C++/Workflow</b>: (vl::)presentation::controls::GuiDateComboBox*</li>
                        <li><b>Template Tag</b>: &lt;DateComboBoxTemplate/&gt;</li>
                        <li><b>Template Name</b>: DateComboBox</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>&lt;DateComboBox/&gt;</b> is a combo box control with a <b>&lt;DatePicker/&gt;</b> in the dropdown container.
        </p>
        <topic>
            <title>&lt;DateComboBox&gt; Properties</title>
            <topic>
                <title>SelectedDate (SelectedDateChanged)</title>
                <p>
                    The default value is the today provided by the OS.
                </p>
                <p>
                    When a day is selected from the <b>&lt;DatePicker/&gt;</b> in the dropdown container,
                    <b>SelectedDate</b> and <b>Text</b> will be updated,
                </p>
            </topic>
            <topic>
                <title>DatePicker</title>
                <p>
                    The <b>&lt;DatePicker/&gt;</b> control in the dropdown container.
                </p>
            </topic>
        </topic>
    </topic>
</article>